00:31:32.566 --> 00:31:33.542
AUDIENCE: 4, C?

00:31:33.542 --> 00:31:34.720
PROFESSOR: 4, C?

00:31:34.720 --> 00:31:36.330
All right, let's see that.

00:31:36.330 --> 00:31:39.570
Where's C-- whoa, yeah.

00:31:39.570 --> 00:31:43.510
C has the hots for
