00:32:36.380 --> 00:32:38.650
works like this, that
works, that's known to work,

00:32:38.650 --> 00:32:40.569
where you start
patching things up,

00:32:40.569 --> 00:32:42.110
because as you're
patching things up,

00:32:42.110 --> 00:32:45.610
you might make other things
